description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports necessary modules such as React, ReactDOM, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by creating a root element and rendering the App component within React's StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React component tree.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component hierarchy into the root DOM node.
